listings.description: Private setting on over 3 1/2 acres with beautiful hilltop view of both sunrise and sunsets. Well built 'liteform' home offers lower insurance and lower heating and cooling costs. The main floor features a formal living room with vaulted ceilings and a fireplace, a spacious kitchen with an island and ample counter space, a formal dining room, and a sunroom that opens to a private deck. The primary suite is located on the main level and includes a large bath with a jetted tub and walk-in closet. Upstairs is an additional bedroom and bath, while the finished basement offers a large living area, bedroom with egress, and excellent storage space. 5 heated garage spaces.

If you love luxury and care-free living, this one and a half story, Dakota Dunes (Willows), is for you. Exterior Stucco, new composite deck off the back of the home overlooking beautiful trees, donning vibrant fall colors. Sliders to the deck. Enjoy high ceilings, wood flooring in the living and dining rooms, stunning marble entryway, tile flooring in the kitchen with gorgeous custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, pantry with a coffee bar, main floor laundry, half bath with new wallpaper. The master bedroom is newly painted.

Have you ever wanted to own a historical home without all of the work to renovate? This one is sure to impress! Sitting on a large, corner lot, this property offers 4 units (over 4400 finished sq. ft.) with a full basement and coin op. laundry room. This is a great addition to your investment portfolio, or a new place to call home. Numerous updates have been done including refinished hardwood floors, new carpet and flooring, paint, appliances, and heat pump mini splits in each unit for efficient heating and cooling.

Discover Your Dream Home in Woodbury Heights! This wonderful Ranch home features a spacious master bedroom with a skylight, a walk-in closet, a private bath, and new carpet. Additionally, there are two more bedrooms on the main level; one also has new carpet, and the other is currently being utilized as a main floor laundry area, but it is easily converted back to a bedroom. There are additional laundry hook ups available in the lower level and both laundry rooms are fully furnished.

You are going to love this home. There are 4 bedrooms up, 3 1/2 baths, it has a formal dining room, den or office space, great eat-in kitchen open to the living room, woodburning fireplace. Family room, 5th bedroom, 3/4 bath, and a den down, a porch, deck, 2 car attached garage, located on a cul-de-sac. Close to schools and shopping.

Fully Updated 3 bedroom 3.5 bathroom 2 story home. Just a blocks from bus stop, hospital, shopping and schools. Hang your jacket in the breezeway just before stepping into the foyer of your newly updated home. Off the foyer you will find an updated Half Bath, Dinning Room, Living Room, Kitchen, and Four Season Room. The Kitchen features new paint, flooring, cabinets, counter tops, windows and lighting. New carpet and flooring will lead you upstairs to three bedrooms, and a new 3/4 bath.

Welcome to this freshly updated meticulously cared for 2 bedroom, 1 bath home nestled in the heart of Morningside, one of Sioux City's most sought after neighborhoods. This cozy property offers all the essentials with a rare 4 stall heated garage with triple insulation and upstairs storage in back that's perfect for car enthusiasts, hobbyists, or anyone needing extra storage. It has extra off street parking and is on a paved alley. It also has an 8x8 storage shed and a patio with an electric awning for shade.

Welcome home to 1839 Indian Hills Drive - A conveniently located 2 bedroom condo that includes TWO garage spaces, ideal for secure parking, storage, or hobbies. On the main floor, you'll find a functional kitchen with a large pantry, ideal for storage and everyday cooking. The kitchen flows into the open living and dining area, creating a warm and inviting space for gatherings or quiet evenings at home. Sliding doors lead to a fenced-in back patio, offering a private outdoor space perfect for relaxing, grilling, or container gardening.

Nice Well Maintained 3 Bedroom, Updated kitchen and Bath, Hardwood Floors, 2 Stall garage. Newer Roof and Water Heater. Great Enclosed Porch, Double Glass Doors from the Kitchen to the Deck. Fenced Yard, Move in Ready.

Build your future on this 1.22-acre residential lot located on Old Lakeport Road in Sergeant Bluff. The property is within the Sergeant Bluff-Luton School District and has access to city water and city sewer at the street. This level lot features plenty of mature trees, offering natural beauty and privacy.
HUD HOMES are Sold AS IS. SUBMIT OFFERS AT HUDHOMESTORE.GOV. CASE# 161-372445.

Nice 2 + Bedroom 1 & 3/4 Baths 3 Garage stalls, Fenced Yard. Main floor Laundry. Lots of potential but does need some work. This house was built prior to 1978 so Lead Base Paint potential exists. House is selling AS IS.

Welcome to this split-level home located in Northside Sioux City. This gorgeous property features new flooring, laundry on lower level, New paint throughout the interior. The downstairs has been converted into a separate unit to be rented out but can easily be converted back to additional space for the new homeowners. The backyard is ample with mature trees so you can enjoy the shade in the summertime; it also has a great big privacy fence!
The lots are ready to dig in 30 days. Buyers to sign Storm Water Agreement; see attached documents.
